  "description": {
    "en": {
      "provenance": "imported",
      "value": "1.       Technical and financial support provided to department of health services to revise and update immunization , IMCI, newborn , safemotherhood, nutrition ,emergency nutrition  and FCHV  polices and strategies with focus on reaching the most disadvantaged\r\n2.       High level policy and advocacy meetings related to MNCH, nutrition and SWAp  coordinated and supported.\r\n3.       Provide technical and financial support to develop MNH referral system guidelines to ensure equitable access for the socially excluded and marginalized groups  \r\n4.       Technical assistance, financial and coordination support provided to NPC, MoHP and nutrition stakeholders for multi sectoral nutrition approach.\r\nInvestment case focussing on equity develped using MBB tool for annual work planning and budgetting for ministry of health."
    },
